FBIS4-49926 "drchi092_k_94012" FBIS-CHI-94-092 Daily Report 12 May 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Police Arrest Shanghai Dissident Yang Zhou Police Arrest Shanghai Dissident Yang Zhou HK1205090394 Hong Kong AFP in English 0829 GMT 12 May 94 HK1205090394 Hong Kong AFP English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 12 (AFP)--Police in Shanghai have arrested Yang Zhou, spokesman of the Chinese Association for Human Rights, his wife said Thursday. "Four policemen came to our home around midday. They took away my husband after searching the house and taking away documents," the wife, Li Guoping, said by phone. It is the fifth arrest of a Shanghai dissident in a month.
